On this page

On This Day in History ​

1. Basic Usage ​

Access the following URL to retrieve historical events for the current day:

txt
https://zeapi.ink/v1/today.php
1

2. Specific Date Query ​

Add query parameters to specify a month and day:

txt
https://zeapi.ink/v1/today.php?month=7&day=4
1

4. Response Fields Description ​

FieldTypeDescription
statusstringRequest status (success/error)
messagestringOperation result message
data.datestringQueried date (month and day)
data.eventsarrayList of historical events

Event Object Fields:

FieldTypeDescription
yearintOriginal year (negative for BC)
displayYearstringFormatted year (includes "BC" if applicable)
typeintEvent type (1=Event, 2=Birth, 3=Death)
typeTextstringEvent type text
datastringEvent description content
